      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously cared for by a single owner. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs silently, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features function exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it were brand new.",
