      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a well-maintained vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s super clean, runs beautifully, and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
