    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 Audi S4 finished in Daytona Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning driver, offering a spirited 354-hp turbocharged V6 paired with the confidence of Quattro all-wheel drive. The exterior remains sharp and glossy, showing only minor road peppering on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather S-sport seats are in excellent shape, featuring minimal bolster wear and a strictly smoke-free cabin environment. All premium technology features, including the Audi Virtual Cockpit and the Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it comes with a fully documented service history, including a recent synthetic oil service and fresh brake pads. The performance tires have approximately 70% tread remaining on the 19-inch V-spoke wheels. This is a solid, turn-key performance sedan that has been cared for with pride.",
